title: [Shannivar's Outfitting]
[Shannivar's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath a domed white stucco ceiling, a midnight blue rising phoenix tapestry hangs on one of the refined oak-paneled walls.  Some wrought-iron hooks and a series of low oak shelves sit in opposite corners while a thin gold-edge black runner rests on a white limestone floor.

Beneath a domed white stucco ceiling, a snowy forest glade tapestry hangs on one of the refined oak-paneled walls.  Some wrought-iron hooks and a series of low oak shelves sit in opposite corners while a thin gold-edge black runner rests on a white limestone floor.
